{"status":200,"code":1000,"message":null,"timestamp":"1762173307802","path":null,"data":{"id":2912,"title":"ManuLife:推出「宏摯傳承保障計劃」及相關事宜","type":"PRODUCT_PROMOTION","time":1713756040529,"tags":["宏利保險"],"content":"<p>致合作夥伴:</p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<strong> 一、新產品推出</strong></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2024-04-22/blobid0_a65f61625c8a40de9aca23be3063cd2d.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">ManuLife於<span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #fc0c16;\"><strong>2024年4月22日</strong></span>推出<strong><span style=\"color: #179e11;\">「宏摯傳承保障計劃」</span></strong>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 本計劃是一個全面及具有競爭力的產品，具有<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #179e11; text-decoration: underline;\">高回報率</span></span>及<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #179e11; text-decoration: underline;\">快回本</span></span>，預期總內部回報率<strong>最高可達<span style=\"color: #fc0c16;\">7.19%</span></strong>；</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 此外，亦提供<strong><span style=\"color: #fc0c16;\">優化</span></strong>的<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #179e11; text-decoration: underline;\">身故賠償支付選項和新保單服務</span></span>，以進一步加強次計劃作為財富保值和傳承的全方位財富傳承解決方案。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>二、客戶推廣優惠</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 於推廣期<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #fc0c16; text-decoration: underline;\">2024年4月22日至6月30日(包括首尾兩天)</span></strong></span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">內成功投保，</span><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">並達指定年度化保費</strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">，</span></p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>3年繳</strong>，可享首個保單年度<strong><span style=\"color: #179e11;\">高達15%</span>保費折扣優惠</strong></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>5年繳</strong>，可享首2個保單年度<strong><span style=\"color: #179e11;\">合共</span><span style=\"color: #179e11;\">高達22%</span>保費折扣優惠</strong></span></li>\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>5年繳</strong>，預繳保費享每年<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder; color: #179e11;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">5.5%</span></span><strong>保證利息</strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #f316ca; font-size: 8pt;\">(推廣期至5月31日)</span></span></span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>10/15年繳</strong>，<strong><span style=\"color: #179e11;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: 400;\">可享首2個保單年度</span><strong style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"color: #179e11;\">合共</span></strong>高達25%</span>保費折扣優惠</strong></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>三、其他產品動態</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1).<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>「創富傳承保障計劃2」</strong></span>及<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>「盈傳創富保障計劃2」</strong></span>將於<strong><span style=\"color: #fc0c16;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">2024年5月21日</span>停售</span></strong>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2).<strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">「歲稅樂享延期年金」</span>建議書更新</strong>，在<strong>「建議書摘要中第2.3部分」</strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">新增了摘要列表</span>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3).於<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #fc0c16; text-decoration: underline;\">2024年4月22日起</span></strong></span>，<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>「宏利晉逸自願醫保附加計劃」可附加至「精選定期壽險」</strong></span>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 詳情請參閱附件。</span></p>","attachments":[{"fileName":"NewsFlash_20240419.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2024-04-22/NewsFlash_20240419_482c1d9e314a469fb047abe18bb6ffd2.pdf","uploadTime":1713753394721,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"宏摯傳承保障計劃_優惠單張.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2024-04-22/宏摯傳承保障計劃_優惠單張_92ac093ba1c943cbba30137e2ba8770d.pdf","uploadTime":1713753513863,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"預繳保費推廣優惠.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2024-04-22/預繳保費推廣優惠_754ab9c819354ba5b1d1e54d7b1c6ff0.pdf","uploadTime":1713753769242,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"提前繳付4年保費安排申請表.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2024-04-22/提前繳付4年保費安排申請表_4d64f9c72a4c4e74a3c96638ce6c2793.pdf","uploadTime":1713753774183,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null}],"companyCode":"MANULIFE","com